Pokedex
Getting up close to a Koffing will give you a chance to observe, through its thin skin, the toxic gases swirling inside. It blows up at the slightest stimulation.
By diluting its toxic gases with a special process, the highest grade of perfume can be extracted. To Filtring, gases emanating from garbage are the ultimate feast.
Weezing alternately shrinks and inflates its twin bodies to mix together toxic gases inside. The more the gases are mixed, the more powerful the toxins become. The {PKMN} also becomes more putrid.
